high_descs: Move to the white table on the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table.
Cut up the apple that is also on the table.
Turn to the left and move to the microwave across the room.
Place the knife inside the microwave and close the door.
Turn around and head back to the small white table next to the dishwasher.
Pick up an apple slice off of the table.
Turn around and move across the kitchen to the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave.  Cook the apple.  Take the apple out of the microwave. Close the door.
Turn around and cross the room to the refrigerator.
Place the apple inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice and apple to be cooked in the microwave to be placed into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the kitchen table so that you are facing where the tomato and knife are.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the table behind the apple.
Slice the apple that is on the table.
Turn to the left, walk to the end of the table, turn left again, walk forward a few steps, then turn right to walk up to the kitchen counter space where the microwave is.
Place the butter knife in the microwave.
Turn around, move forward a few steps, then hang a left to walk back over to the table with the apple.
Pick up a piece of the apple from the table.
Turn left, walk to the end of the table, then turn left again, moving forward a few steps before you turn right to walk over to the microwave.
Heat the apple slice up in the microwave before taking it back out.
Turn around completely, walk forward, hanging a left once you reach the wall, then walk up to the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice into the fridge.
